# =============================================================================
# Frontend environment (Vite — variables must be prefixed with VITE_)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local dev: copy to `frontend/.env.local` (gitignored) if you need overrides.
#
# Render — Static Site: Dashboard → your static site → Environment
#   Add at build time:
#     VITE_API_URL=https://YOUR-API-SERVICE.onrender.com
#   Use your Web Service (Express API) public URL — NOT the static site URL.
#   No trailing slash. Example: https://agc-member-portal.onrender.com
#
# After changing VITE_* vars, trigger a new deploy so `npm run build` picks them up.
# =============================================================================

# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com
